text: Jamie Lowell (born May 2, 2002) is an American soccer player who plays as a goalkeeper for USL Championship side Tacoma Defiance and the Seattle Sounders FC academy. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:American soccer players Category:Tacoma Defiance players Category:USL Championship players Category:Soccer players from New Hampshire Category:2002 births Category:Living people
